summary: Olfrid Battle-Born now holds a unique key. A key to his hidden Stash behind Battle-Born Farm. You now have two choices: Steal the key, or pick the expert lock. What lies inside is his War-Axe, and some other randomized goods.
descriptionHtml: Olfrid Battle-Born now holds a unique key. A key to his hidden Stash behind Battle-Born Farm. You now have two choices: Steal the key, or pick the expert lock. What lies inside is his War-Axe, and some other randomized goods. The stash is no more than a mere chest, as this is my first Mod. Sorry if you expected a challenging, trap-filled, dungeon. Maybe later.
author: williewest10
